    title = '{"tr": "Künye", "en": "Imprint", "de": "Impressum"}'::jsonb,
    content = '{
        "de": "<h1>Impressum</h1><p><strong>Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG</strong></p><p>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen<br>Deutschland</p><p><strong>Kontakt</strong><br>E-Mail: kontakt@kolaydugun.de</p><p><strong>Verantwortlich für den Inhalt nach § 55 Abs. 2 RStV</strong><br>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen</p><p><strong>Streitschlichtung</strong><br>Die Europäische Kommission stellt eine Plattform zur Online-Streitbeilegung (OS) bereit: <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.<br>Unsere E-Mail-Adresse finden Sie oben im Impressum.<br>Wir sind nicht bereit oder verpflichtet, an Streitbeilegungsverfahren vor einer Verbraucherschlichtungsstelle teilzunehmen.</p>",
        "en": "<h1>Imprint</h1><p><strong>Information according to § 5 TMG</strong></p><p>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen<br>Germany</p><p><strong>Contact</strong><br>E-Mail: kontakt@kolaydugun.de</p><p><strong>Responsible for content according to § 55 Abs. 2 RStV</strong><br>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen</p><p><strong>Dispute Resolution</strong><br>The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (OS): <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.<br>You can find our email address in the imprint above.<br>We are not willing or obliged to participate in dispute resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.</p>",
        "tr": "<h1>Künye</h1><p><strong>§ 5 TMG uyarınca bilgiler</strong></p><p>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen<br>Almanya</p><p><strong>İletişim</strong><br>E-posta: kontakt@kolaydugun.de</p><p><strong>§ 55 Abs. 2 RStV uyarınca içerikten sorumlu</strong><br>Hamza Karabulut<br>Schützenstraße 1<br>89269 Vöhringen</p><p><strong>Uyuşmazlık Çözümü</strong><br>Avrupa Komisyonu, çevrimiçi uyuşmazlık çözümü (OS) için bir platform sunmaktadır: <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.<br>E-posta adresimizi yukarıda bulabilirsiniz.<br>Bir tüketici hakem heyeti önünde uyuşmazlık çözümü prosedürlerine katılmaya istekli veya yükümlü değiliz.</p>"
    }'::jsonb
